data.text:
Product Feature And Application

Application

High Conversion of Energy

Upgraded high-density monocrystalline silicon solar panels convert up to 23% more energy.Use the sun's rays to power your devices from anywhere.

DC Powerful Output

With a DC 120W output, it can also charge automobile batteries and accumulators, and the port's wide compatibility is sufficient to fulfill your charging demands in the outdoors.

Design that is long-lasting

The canvas fabric and fine stitching are tough enough for outdoor use.The ETFE polymer coating, which guarantees IPX4 waterproofing, makes the panels resistant to water and dust.

Safe Charging Security

Smart dentification of your devices and different gadgets is built-in to provide the best charging speed.Overcharge, overheating, and short circuit protection ensure 100% safe charging.
